de.bpmnaftool.model.aristaflow.activity
Class XorActivity

java.lang.Object
  de.bpmnaftool.model.aristaflow.activity.ActivityTemplateImpl
      de.bpmnaftool.model.aristaflow.activity.XorActivity
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActivityTemplate
public class XorActivity
extends ActivityTemplateImpl

Implementation of an XorActivity. This activity is a so called decision activity. It is used for exclusive split nodes and end loop node and makes the decision which edge to take. This implementation can not generate decision byte code, so it stores it for up to 10 activities.

Author:
Felix Härer
